detail.name: Babidi
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 1 <Majin Buu> or card with 《Wicked Soul》 in its special traits and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of its owner's deck in a random order.

detail.name: バビディ
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分のデッキの上から5枚を見て、「魔人ブウ」か特徴《邪心》を持つカード1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
